---
import Cta from '../../components/home/Cta-Contact.astro';
import SlotHero from '../../components/home/Slot-Hero.astro';
import SectionHeadImg from "../../components/home/slot-img.astro";
import SectionHeadSecImg from "../../components/home/slot-img-rev.astro";
import Process from '../../components/home/Process.astro';
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro';
---

<Layout
  description="For over 6 years we have specialised in UX-focused web design. Promoting user experience design choices to improve monthly sales. Highly branded website design that doesn't sacrifice on user experience is the fastest way for small businesses to become memorable brands in our opinion."
  title="UX Design Â· Web Design by Aidxn Design"
>

    <SlotHero>
      <Fragment slot="smltitle">
        Gold Coast User Experience Design
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="title">
        UX-Focused Web Design.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="desc">
        For over 6 years we have specialised in UX-focused web design. Promoting user experience design choices to improve monthly sales. Highly branded website design that doesn't sacrifice on user experience is the fastest way for small businesses to become memorable brands in our opinion.
      </Fragment>
      <Fragment slot="cover">
        <img
                  src="/works/br-mac-render-med.webp"
                  class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                />
      </Fragment>
    </SlotHero>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              E-commerce conversion rate optimisation
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              Sell more online everyday.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              Looking for top-notch Gold Coast Wordpress design services to boost your online business? Look no further than Aidxn Design! With over six years of experience in optimizing conversion rates for Wordpress stores and funnels, we're your go-to experts for creating stunning and user-friendly e-commerce websites. Our primary focus is on UX design, ensuring that your customers have a seamless and enjoyable shopping experience from start to finish.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/br-mac-render-med.webp"
                        class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>

          <SectionHeadSecImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              Improving conversion rate through design
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              An expert in improving funnel conversion rate.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              At Aidxn Design, we understand the unique needs of businesses in the Gold Coast area. Our team of experienced professionals will work closely with you to create a customized Wordpress store that not only looks fantastic but also drives results. Whether you're looking to revamp your existing online store or start from scratch, our Gold Coast Wordpress design services are tailored to meet your specific goals and objectives. We use proven strategies and cutting-edge design techniques to help you stand out in the competitive e-commerce landscape.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/hero-estem.webp"
                        class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadSecImg>

          <SectionHeadImg>
            <Fragment slot="smltitle">
              In-person web design revisions
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="title">
              UX optimisation, done in-person.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="desc">
              Understanding technology is hard enough when you're not working around it 24/7. That why our business model is heavily designed around swapping video calls for face-to-face meetings. Offering our Oxenford office as a place to meet and revise your brand and UX saves hours of text message back and forth.
            </Fragment>
            <Fragment slot="cover">
              <img
                        src="/works/br-mac-render-med.webp"
                        class="w-full rounded duration-200 hover:shadow-sm"
                      />
            </Fragment>
          </SectionHeadImg>
  
  <Process />
  <Cta />

</Layout>
